  "Description": {
    "English": "A specialist optical component. Employing an impossibly polished surface, this mirror is able to selectively filter different wavelengths of light, changing its reflective pattern based on nearby magnetic fields.<br><br>Used in the creation of a wide range of <span class=\"name name-technology\">advanced technologies</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种专业的光学部件。该镜采用极端抛光的表面，能够选择性地过滤不同波长的光，并根据附近的磁场改变反射模式。<br><br>可用于创造各种<span class=\"name name-technology\">高级技术</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "專家級光學元件。表面光滑毫無瑕疵，這面鏡子能夠選擇性的過濾不同波長的光線，並根據週遭的磁場而改變反射規則。<br><br>能用來製造各式<span class=\"name name-technology\">先進科技</span>。"
  },
