  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft Solar Mirror from <span class=\"name name-earth\">Gold</span>, <span class=\"name name-earth\">Silver</span> and <span class=\"name name-special\">Chromatic Metal</span>.<br><br><span class=\"name name-earth\">Gold</span> and <span class=\"name name-earth\">Silver</span> are valuable interstellar trading minerals, most commonly <span class=\"name name-commodity\">mined from asteroids</span>. They are occasionally found in underground planetary deposits.<br><span class=\"name name-special\">Chromatic Metal</span> is created in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span> from the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">stellar metals</span>: <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Copper</span>, <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Cadmium</span>, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Emeril</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">Indium</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "用<span class=\"name name-earth\">金</span>、<span class=\"name name-earth\">银</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">有色金属</span>制作太阳能镜。<br><br><span class=\"name name-earth\">金</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">银</span>是珍贵的星际交易矿物，通常<span class=\"name name-commodity\">从小行星开采</span>得到。有时可在行星地下矿床中发现。<br><span class=\"name name-special\">有色金属</span>可采用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>从<span class=\"name name-stellar\">恒星金属</span>中制得：<span class=\"name name-commodity\">铜</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">镉</span>、<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">艾梅里尔</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">铟</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "以<span class=\"name name-earth\">金</span>、<span class=\"name name-earth\">銀</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">有色金屬</span>製作日鏡。<br><br><span class=\"name name-earth\">金</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">銀</span>是非常珍貴的星際交易礦物，通常<span class=\"name name-commodity\">從小行星開採而來</span>。有時能在星球地底資源產地找到。<br><span class=\"name name-special\">有色金屬</span>是以<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>加工以下<span class=\"name name-stellar\">星體金屬</span>而成：<span class=\"name name-commodity\">銅</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">鎘</span>、<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">砪</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">銦</span>。"
  },
